{"tid":469088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：跳蟲啟發　港大發明新防水料 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-11-15T03:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T04:09:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e594cf8f16b12188e431e999cd5995b6bc8c8700","tid":469088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171115/20215015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F20215015&d=dVuD9CyTRKGt4QCszSyEAmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=47a0ee81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F20215015&h=b9f31b8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171115/20215015</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：跳蟲啟發　港大發明新防水料 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171115/large/15lp2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F15lp2p4.jpg&h=da1dac9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大噚日公佈成功研發廉價防水防油物料。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥話要推創科產業，其實香港大專院校不時有唔少創科研發成果公佈。好似港大噚日公佈成功研發廉價環保防水防油物料，只要將呢啲特製物料覆蓋係其他物料上面，就可以有防水同防油的效果，日後可以用嚟做衫，甚至用係軍事用途。<br />\n<br />\n負責呢個研究項目嘅港大機械工程系博士朱平安話，呢種物料意念係來自跳蟲，因為跳蟲棲息係泥土入面，經常會遇上雨水淹浸，所以進化出能抵抗泥土摩擦、又有良好排水能力嘅角質表皮，研究團隊就係模仿跳蟲表皮結構，設計出呢種耐摩擦又防水嘅物料。香港大學工程學院機械工程系教授王立話，呢種物料如果大量生產，每平方米只需港幣7毫至1.3元，比其他防水物料平好多。"},{"pid":"1da2e115aab64d5bfabdcd3dd38d8ee31318a82a","tid":469088,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9501aa0c0e0cfc343336b047ed4483f507674d","tid":469088,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21db0091a1a111b60b28e8d63292bc2c7d2f351b","tid":469088,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27eacf174431ba882ae1aec7f18a98ac48225df5","tid":469088,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"宜家香港D大學搞研究果班大把大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5301e46fd880f708b932455538ad0f0417f31f04","tid":469088,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/120737_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F120737_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60e8b44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係冇估錯，就連下面果個港大機械工程系教授都係大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大陸人對香港科研作出偉大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}